36#include "krb5_locl.h"
37
38#ifndef HEIMDAL_SMALLER
39#define DES3_OLD_ENCTYPE 1
40#endif
41
42struct _krb5_checksum_type *_krb5_checksum_types[] = {
43 &_krb5_checksum_none,
44#ifdef HEIM_WEAK_CRYPTO
45 &_krb5_checksum_crc32,
46 &_krb5_checksum_rsa_md4,
47 &_krb5_checksum_rsa_md4_des,
48 &_krb5_checksum_rsa_md5_des,
49#endif
50#ifdef DES3_OLD_ENCTYPE
51 &_krb5_checksum_rsa_md5_des3,
52#endif
53 &_krb5_checksum_rsa_md5,
54 &_krb5_checksum_sha1,
55 &_krb5_checksum_hmac_sha1_des3,
56 &_krb5_checksum_hmac_sha1_aes128,
57 &_krb5_checksum_hmac_sha1_aes256,
58 &_krb5_checksum_hmac_sha256_128_aes128,
59 &_krb5_checksum_hmac_sha384_192_aes256,
60 &_krb5_checksum_hmac_md5
61};
62
63int _krb5_num_checksums
64 = sizeof(_krb5_checksum_types) / sizeof(_krb5_checksum_types[0]);
65
66/*
67 * these should currently be in reverse preference order.
68 * (only relevant for !F_PSEUDO) */
69
70struct _krb5_encryption_type *_krb5_etypes[] = {
71 &_krb5_enctype_aes256_cts_hmac_sha384_192,
72 &_krb5_enctype_aes128_cts_hmac_sha256_128,
73 &_krb5_enctype_aes256_cts_hmac_sha1,
74 &_krb5_enctype_aes128_cts_hmac_sha1,
75 &_krb5_enctype_des3_cbc_sha1,
76 &_krb5_enctype_des3_cbc_none, /* used by the gss-api mech */
77 &_krb5_enctype_arcfour_hmac_md5,
78#ifdef DES3_OLD_ENCTYPE
79 &_krb5_enctype_des3_cbc_md5,
80 &_krb5_enctype_old_des3_cbc_sha1,
81#endif
82#ifdef HEIM_WEAK_CRYPTO
83 &_krb5_enctype_des_cbc_md5,
84 &_krb5_enctype_des_cbc_md4,
85 &_krb5_enctype_des_cbc_crc,
86 &_krb5_enctype_des_cbc_none,
87 &_krb5_enctype_des_cfb64_none,
88 &_krb5_enctype_des_pcbc_none,
89#endif
90 &_krb5_enctype_null
91};
92
93int _krb5_num_etypes = sizeof(_krb5_etypes) / sizeof(_krb5_etypes[0]);
